export enum N2Status {
  DRAFT = 'Draft',
  PENDING_APPROVAL = 'Pending Approval',
  APPROVED = 'Approved',
  ONGOING = 'Ongoing',
  REJECTED = 'Rejected',
  PENDING_TERMINATED = 'Pending Termination',
  TERMINATED = 'Terminated',
  PENDING_INVALIDATION = 'Pending Invalidation',
  INVALIDATED = 'Invalidated',
  SUCCESSFUL = 'Successful',
  FAILED = 'Failed',
  COMPLETED = 'Completed',
  PENDING_GENERATION = 'Pending Generation',
  GENERATING = 'Generating',
  PROCESSING = 'Processing',
  PROCESSING_RETURN_FILE = 'Processing Retun File',
  ACTIVE = 'Active',
  RESULT_FILE_GENERATION_FAILED = 'Result File Generation Failed',
  PENDING_DOWNLOAD = 'Pending Download',
  PENDING_RETURN = 'Pending Return'
}
